{"tid":702400,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股壇傳奇】逾4.4億遺產 養子為唯一受益人","createTime":"2018-06-15T01:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T03:43:48.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f835d02fda197a4673685bae45344e0732f5c11d","tid":702400,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180614/large/1528981904_8973.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180614%2Flarge%2F1528981904_8973.jpg&h=bbfec6dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳普芬遺產由其養子陳德標成為唯一受益人。<br />\n<br />\n股壇傳奇人物業陳普芬4年前去世，留下價值至少1.7億元的現金、股票及公司股份由其養子陳德標管理，若渣甸山故居以叫價2.7億元沽出，遺產總值超過4.4億元。<br />\n<br />\n陳普芬妻子2007年2月因病於鄧肇堅醫院逝世，享年81歲。失去老伴，與家庭傭工居住渣甸山逾3000方呎大屋。數年前，有報道指他兒子長居美國。2014年3月陳普芬仙遊，根據文件，留下數以億計的遺產，包括銀行港元及外幣現金存款涉及約9,229萬元；19隻股票按本周三計市值超過8,000萬元；4間公司股份包括人和證券、陳普芬會計師有限公司、駿輝會計有限公司、Buddy Electronics &amp; Systems Limited。2014年年底，法庭接獲申請遺產管理書，陳德標為遺產管理人。2015年3月法庭認可陳德標為陳普芬養子(Lawful Adopted Son)，並為唯一遺產受益人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180615/58319230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58319230&d=bNbl%2FLWCCKDu5uVJf5jIbUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a066b7c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58319230&h=d0b5944c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180615/58319230</a>"},{"pid":"2f37fd641f0faa87a526bc9bca383af0712f200b","tid":702400,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce90666109c86c229d862de43ed2a1bf7439964","tid":702400,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:00:44.000Z","msg":"養子前世做左咩好事"},{"pid":"c976bf6fb2276f986c1cb4052dd4aa7789a6aae4","tid":702400,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"Let be my sugar daddy<br />\nMy sugar daddy<br />\n<br />\n利申: FFX"},{"pid":"6e6dda00ab0311da9a6dcdcb5fbadfc50f43b5c4","tid":702400,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"Lets be my sugar daddy<br />\nMy sugar daddy<br />\n只得你最讓我安心<br />\n請給我送贈貴重禮物<br />\n如財富或金銀 只想收租過一生<br />\nLets be my sugar daddy<br />\nMy sugar daddy<br />\n今晚要結局你一生<br />\n終於可說句 「Yours are mine」<br />\n帶上這介子 手不鬆開不掉低我 (未改)<br />\nI'm your honey (未改)"}]}